&lt;li&gt;Initiate or support various projects in your territory, that can range from complex negotiations with our partners to specific marketing initiatives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Represent the company at industry events, trade shows, and conferences to enhance brand visibility and generate new opportunities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who You Are:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
