&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;Leadership of Channels &amp;amp; Digital Pipeline Operations&lt;/span&gt;:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;You will own all digital&amp;nbsp;channels:&amp;nbsp;paid, owned, earned and optimize them end-to-end for awareness, engagement, and conversion.&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
